10 gṛham punar āgacchati, atra tatra ca cintaṃ karoti,
11 yathā durdaivī yaḥ na jānāti kim kartavyam;
12 tataḥ punar āgacchati, āśā ca punar āgacchati,

16 Evam mama gurur mama cittaṃ bhayena vyākulīcakāra
17 yadā aham tam evam ākulaṃ lalāṭaṃ apaśyam,
18 ca evam āśu auṣadhaṃ āgataṃ vyādhiṃ prati;

28 ekasya vṛkṣasya, anyām śākhām ālokayām āsa,
29 evam uktvā: "Asyāḥ upari tataḥ āruhya tiṣṭha;
30 api tu pūrvam parīkṣasva kim sā tvām dhārayiṣyati uta neti."

40 āvaśyakam ekasya pārśvasya utthānam anyasya ca avataraṇam;
41 tathāpi vayam ante āgatāḥ sma tasmin age,
42 yatra antimaḥ śilākhaṇḍaḥ niścyavati.

46 "Tvayi evam eva viviktaḥ syāt,"
47 ācāryaḥ uvāca; "yadi sukhopari śayyām karoṣi,
48 kīrtau na āgacchasi, na ca vastreṇa;

55 Dīrghīyaḥ śreṇīḥ ārohaṇīyā;
56 naivetyeṣāṃ vinivṛttiḥ paryāptaḥ.
57 Yadi mama vākyam abhijānāsi, tadā tvam etena sādhayasva.”

67 Na jānāmi kim avocat, yadyapi aham āsīt
68 tataḥ pāre dhanuṣaḥ yat vartate tatra;
69 yaḥ tu avocat sa kopāya pravṛtta iva āsa.

70 Ahaṃ avatīrṇo 'bhavam, api tu jīvantī mama cakṣuṣī
71 na śaknate gantum adhastāt tamaḥprakṛteḥ;
72 atas ahaṃ: "He Guro, kuru yathā tvam āgaccheḥ

73 anyasmāt tīrāt, avaṭarāma ca prākāraṃ;
74 yathā aham atra śṛṇomi na ca jānāmi,
75 tathā adhastāt paśyāmi, na ca kiṃcid avagacchāmi."

85 Na punaḥ sva-valibhir abhimanyeta Lībyā;
86 yadi hi khalu khalidrān, ākulān, phaṇīn,
87 prajanayati, cenkrān saha amphisibena-jātibhiḥ,

94 sarpabhiḥ hastau paścād babaddhāḥ āsīt;
95 tāḥ sarpaḥ svān puccān mūrdhānaṃ ca
96 katiṣu praveśya agre samyojitāḥ āsīt.

100 Na O iti na ca I iti kadācid api tathā likhitam,
101 yathā sa prakadito babhūva dagdho babhūva, sarvaś ca bhasmābhūtaḥ
102 patitvā abhavat;

106 Evam hi mahattamais triṣiṣṭam
107 yaḥ śakunaḥ śyenah mriyate punar jāyate ca,
108 yadā pañcaśatam varṣāṇy upaiti;

121 Tataḥ sa nāyakaḥ tam papraccha kaḥ saḥ syāt;
122 tasmāt sa uvāca: "Aham Tuṣkāra-deśād apatapam,
123 alpam kālam pūrvam, asmin ghora-tale.

127 Ahaṃ ca netre: "Mā tu maunaṃ kuru,
128 Pṛcchasi ca kena pāpena ayam adhastāt patitaḥ;
129 Ahaṃ hi enam kṣatajaviṣaṇṇaṃ paśyāmi."

130 Tataśca pāpī yaḥ śrutvā na samācchādayat,
131 Kim tu mayy eva manaś cakṣuś ca nyavedayat,
132 Duḥkha-lajyayā ca svayam alipyata;

136 Na śaknomi pratiṣedhituṃ yattvam पृच्छसि;
137 Adhastādhiṣṭhitaḥasmi yataḥahamāsmi
138 cauraḥ devalayasya sundarāṇāṃ vastūnāṃ,

142 Vikurva karṇau mama vāṇīṃ prati, śṛṇu ca.
143 Pistoia pūrvam Neri-bhyaḥ kṣīṇā bhaviṣyati;
144 tataḥ Fiorenza jana-padānāṃ ācāra-śīlāni punar api navīkaroti.

145 Marteḥ śaktiḥ Val di Magra-deśāt megha-rūpeṇa āgacchati
146 yaḥ samrambhiṇī-megha-gaṇair āvṛtaḥ asti;
147 caṇḍa-pracaṇḍa-vāyu-sahitaḥ

148 Campo Piceno-nāma-sthale yuddhaṃ bhaviṣyati;
149 yataḥ sa aśanayā megha-gaṇān vihāya niḥsarati,
150 yathā sarve api White-nāmānaḥ tena vidhvaṃsitāḥ bhavanti.
